game.name: Jeff The Killer VS Slendrina
game.description:
Being the fearesome and twisted Slendrina, you cannot afford hearing the praising words for Jeff the killer. So you have decided to clear him from the picture. Is it a right time to take care of this difficult job? If yes, join Jeff the Killer VS Slendrina and gear up to defeat Jeff the killer and his evil companions. You can also play as Jeff the killer to change your mood. As a Jeff, you have to eliminate Slendrina and her evil companions. 
It will be amazing to see these two evil and dastardly villains fighting with each other in this free online zombie game. Use the map to move around the screen and find out all the hidden objects! Grab your weapon and get ready to fight against other iconic character in this epic third person shooter battle! There are various other monsters and creatures to deal with. The top portion of the screen will show your objective in this 3D horror adventure game.
Track your health by looking at the left bottom of the screen. The evil creatures will start attacking you when they see on the screen. Try to use your knife wisely to defend yourself against their quick attack! Do not forget to go through the controls before entering this fiercely battle. Guide your chosen character to help make their way towards the win and prove the world that you are a true fighter! Let us see who will win the biggest battle of evil!  Have fun without download on atmegame.com!
